The Diocese of Lagos Anglican Communion has rescheduled the centenary rally fixed for February 23, 2019 to March 2, 2019 as a result of the postponement of the presidential election earlier fixed for February 16, 2019. The centenary rally is part of the programme for the 100 years celebration of the establishment of diocese of Lagos. According to the church, they are expecting all Anglicans to converge at the Main Bowl Tafawa Balewa Square (TBS) Lagos. The 14 Archdeaconries will display their talents and intimate the